      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The engine runs but suffers from frequent overheating and several noticeable fluid leaks, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels, multiple dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. Inside, the upholstery is torn and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are currently non-functional. It is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor.",
