    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects meticulous, single-owner stewardship. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously scrutinized to ensure it meets the expectations of the most discerning collector. This is an uncompromising opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless caliber and investment-grade quality.",
