    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, she's in stunning condition\u2014practically looks and smells like she just left the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, and it really shows. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You've gotta see it to believe how clean it is. Shoot me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 43500.0,
