    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains in peak mechanical health, breathing through six individual throttle bodies with the double-VANOS system fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This chassis is structurally pristine, featuring a proactively reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings to maintain original suspension kinematics. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle offers a visceral driving experience with zero deferred maintenance or mechanical compromise.",
